            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="Body Text">Please </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">wait</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> until it </text>downloads to your PC, if<text styleclass="Body Text"> this is the first time you have downloaded that video. </text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If, at a different time, you click to play the same video, it should play immediately from your hard-disk</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Video screen too small?</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If the video area is too small, drag the right and bottom sides of the dialog to increase its size.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Where do the Videos download to?</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The default path is <text styleclass="VariableName">C:\Users\Adam\AppData\Local\PSMotion\Tutorials\</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You can change the download path. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See</text>&#32;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Application-Settings" anchor="App-General" styleclass="T_Menu">Application-Settings &gt; General tab &gt; File Options separator &gt; Tutorial Video Directory</link><text styleclass="T_Menu">.</text></para>
